<h2 id="section-top">Ophthalmology</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=967">Pennine Acute Hospitals NHS Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address"><br/>0161 624 0420</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent8088b99195384811b4ecb6b970bb2859">
</div>
<p><strong>Out-patient services are currently provided at Fairfield General, The Royal Oldham and Birch Hill Hospital.  In addition to this, out-reach community clinics are available in the Tameside and Heywood areas.  Day surgery services are provided at Birch Hill and the Royal Oldham.  In-patient services are only provided at the Royal Oldham.</strong></p></div>
</div>
</div>
